parameters:
Fumika and Makoto were pushed into a room where
the walls, ceiling, and floor were all covered in
tentacles.

I'm already back to my normal form and my whole
body is in tatters.

Why are we being held captive here, Nymphoria? The
tentacles are wriggling all over the walls... As
expected, it's a tasteless room.

Hmph, it's not as good as your slime walls. I'll
make sure to violate them plenty in this room.

Shokushu-ma Shockseal: Well then, shall I violate
these helpless best friends, the two high school
girls, to my heart's content? Kukuku!
Ichijo Fumika: Ugh, please stop it already...

Futaba Makoto: I can't bear being violated like
this by these creatures...

Shokushu-ma Shockseal: Scream all you want! Come
on, tentacles, do your thing!

When Shockseal signaled with her finger, Fumika
and Makoto were immediately entangled in the
tentacles and completely restrained.
